This is the Markdown version of the corresponding chapter at https://ds.cs.luc.edu.

You need to have Pandoc (pandoc) installed on your computer. See https://pandoc.org for details on how to install. Binaries are available for all platforms. Please make sure you use a current version.

The script `build.sh` shows how to generate reStructuredText (.rst) and HTML (.html). 
Both of these formats must build successfully to include your contribution. The final submission will be converted to reStructuredText so we can use Sphinx to build your chapter.

More details to come.
